## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources, which may not cover all aspects of child development comprehensively. The information is subject to the limitations of the sources, including potential biases and the date of publication. Additionally, the complexity of child development means that individual experiences may vary significantly, and not all factors can be generalized across different contexts and cultures.